IN Celebrities ON 25 Feb, 2017 Nicki Minaj Finally Attacks On Remy Ma And Trust Me Her Lyrics Are Terrible! Share on twitter Follow Us On

Yeah, and though, a lot of people might not agree to this - "Especially Nicki Minaj's fans," but her lyrics in which she tried to include Remy Ma are nothing but Trash! 
Let's have a look at the complete story! Nicki Minaj Finally Attacks On Remy Ma And Trust Me Her Lyrics Are Terrible! 754 396 Late last year, Bronx wordsmith Remy Ma released her 'Wait A Minute" single remix. Loading... 
Without even anyone telling it, fans were agile to identify the song a diss to Nicki Minaj despite no names were released. Without taking much time... Loading... 
On February 23, Nicki's release of Gucci Mane and Nicki Minaj's "Make Love," it seems that the Queens rapper has lastly announced her slap back. Nicki Minaj attacked Remy Ma's claims. Loading... 
On "Make Love," the mittens are gone as Nicki seems to take a plan at Remy's "queen of rap" challenges and also reaches so far as to confront her opponent to a Nokia phone brutally . Don't did you believe me? Let's have a look at "Make Love's lyrics." Loading... 
"Bitch I'm the greatest, no Kendrick and no Sia/I'm the iPhone, you the Nokia/Everybody know you jealous, bitch it's so clear/Tell them bum ass bitches to play their role," Nicki Minaj's lyrical raps on "Make Love." Nicki has three multi-platinum albums. Loading... 
She also insists that she has the title of rap supremacy as she puts up numbers that other people don't. Fake Breasts controversy. Loading... 
Remy announced same things on "Wait A Minute (Remix)," as she reminds of grabbing "new charges" and wrecked what's supposed to be Nicki atop her "fake breasts." Here's that song which is being released by Nicki Minaj and people are calling it's aimed at Remy Ma.
